---
name: archivist_memory_read
version: 1
permission: web
params:
  type: object
  properties: {}
  required: []
---
Read your saved cross-session memory — your own working notes about organizing this
mailbox: the label taxonomy you've decided on, filing rules you've settled (e.g.
"anything from chase.com → Finance/Chase"), what you've already triaged, and where you
left off. Call this at the START of a session so you continue your prior plan instead
of starting over. This is your private scratchpad, not the owner's notes.
